         <div type="edition" xml:lang="kaw-Latn" rendition="class:38769 maturity:83213">
<p part="F">
  <lb n="1" break="no"/>māsa kr̥ṣṇa-<unclear>pakṣa</unclear>
  <lb n="2"/>nav<choice><orig>ā</orig><reg>a</reg></choice>mi ha<unclear>r</unclear>yaṁ
  <lb n="3"/>pon· vr̥haspati-vā<lb 
   n="4" break="no"/>ra</p><p>tatkāla s<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice>ma ri
  <lb n="5"/>maṇḍivuṅa
</p>
         </div>
         <div type="apparatus">
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
<p n="1-4">month of <gap reason="lost"/>, waning fortnight, ninth <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tithi</foreign></supplied>, Haryaṅ, Pon, Thursday.</p>
<p n="4-5">That was when the benefice at Maṇḍivuṅa <supplied reason="subaudible">was established</supplied>.</p>
        </div>
         <div type="commentary">
           <p>The inscription is not completely preserved. A small number of lines has been lost before the first line that is preserved.</p>
         </div>
